CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 15, 2007

[Cite as 06/15/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-2935.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-2073. Bikkani v. Lee.

Cuyahoga App. No. 88650. Upon consideration of Bikkani’s request for leave to file a motion to enter judgment as satisfied,

It is ordered by the court that leave is granted. Bikkani’s motion to enter judgment as satisfied, which is attached to his request for leave, shall be considered by the court.
